Diary: DATE: March 12th, 2024
Stranger: If you are reading this, it’s already too late for me, but maybe not for you. I started at this company thinking it was a normal cybersecurity firm.
Stranger: What a fool I was. The "Trustlee System" isn't a firewall. It’s a filter. We aren’t hacking companies... we are looking for something. Something that moves between the data.

